#. ~ Description for Xeno's SAS4 weapons pack
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds all the weapons included inside the game SAS4 Zombie assault, only the "
"base quality is present (aka, no red, no black), please do consider that "
"these weapons are not a property of mine, and as that they belong to "
"NInjaKiwi. all of these weapons are a work of finction, and are not in any "
"way related to real guns, launchers or weapons."
